  </table>
  <p>&#160;</p>
  <p><b>Remarks</b> </p>
  <p><span id="Accountable">[1] <i>A: Accountable</i> according to the RACI Model: Those who are ultimately accountable for the correct and thorough completion of the ITIL Technical Management process.</span> </p>
  <p><span id="Responsible">[2] <i>R: Responsible</i> according to the RACI Model: Those who do the work to achieve a task within ITIL Technical Management.</span> </p>
